# Deployment Patterns Overview

## Architecture

Our deployment architecture ensures reliable and consistent releases through:

- CI/CD pipelines
- Environment management
- Release strategies
- Monitoring
- Rollback procedures

## Core Technologies

- GitHub Actions for CI/CD
- Docker for containerization
- Kubernetes for orchestration
- Monitoring tools
- Infrastructure as Code

## Pattern Categories

### 1. CI/CD Pipeline

- Build process
- Testing stages
- Deployment stages
- Quality gates
- Notifications

### 2. Environment Management

- Development
- Staging
- Production
- Feature environments
- Testing environments

### 3. Release Strategy

- Feature flags
- Blue-green deployment
- Canary releases
- Rolling updates
- Rollback procedures

### 4. Infrastructure

- Container orchestration
- Load balancing
- Auto-scaling
- High availability
- Disaster recovery

### 5. Monitoring

- Application metrics
- Infrastructure metrics
- Error tracking
- Performance monitoring
- User analytics

### 6. Security

- Secrets management
- Access control
- Vulnerability scanning
- Compliance checks
- Audit logging

